gov.sandia.cognition.learning.data

Interface RandomizedDataPartitioner<DataType>

  • Type Parameters:
    DataType - The type of data to partition.
    All Superinterfaces:
    DataPartitioner<DataType>, Randomized
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RandomDataPartitioner

    public interface RandomizedDataPartitioner<DataType>
extends DataPartitioner<DataType>, Randomized
    The RandomizedDataPartitioner extends a DataPartitioner to indicate that is it is randomized, which means that its partitions are based (at least in part) on an underlying random number generator.
    Since:
    2.0
